#stance=stance2
#originalStanceText=No
#originalTopic=should-abortion-be-legal
A pro-choice position on any issue should maximize the number of free choices, present and future. The pro-choice position on abortion fails to maximize the number of free choices because it unilaterally eliminates the future free choices of individuals aborted. The pro-life position maximizes the number of free choices because it preserves the present and future free choices of as many individuals as possible without taking away any choices arbitrarily.  